  "page_id": "6442503828",
  "title": "3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行",
  "version": 5,
  "url": "/spaces/CARSFW/pages/6442503828/3.+%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C",
  "last_modified": "2025-11-06T02:40:17.000+01:00",
  "last_modified_by": "CHEN Yongjie (XC-CP/ESW2-CN)",
  "parent_id": "6372329005",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1、 Qualcomm 8775 SAIL Memmap"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "默认情况下，工程里代码和变量都一起加载在SRAM中， SRAM共计3MB。集成协议栈多时，可能SRAM会不够使用，需要分配到DDR区域。"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-26-3.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-26-3.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-26-20.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-26-20.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SRAM 目前前面部分：0x08000000 - 0x080E1000 区域分配给SAIL PBL, EL2_DTB 和EL2(HYP)使用。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "AUTOSAR SW 从 0x080D3800 开始："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-31-35.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-31-35.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-31-51.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-31-51.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-37-8.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-37-8.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2、 通过scatter文件将变量和代码链接到DDR"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "定义新的LR,  SAIL_DDR_DATA 块存放sail_ddr_data段定义的变量；"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SAIL_DDR_Text用来存放代码(和const变量)， 目前测试只将Rte_Task_C0_10ms.c 文件里的代码加载到固定DDR地址：0x20000100."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-47-11.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-47-11.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "测试变量定义方法： 通过 section关键字指定测试变量链接地址"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-51-23.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-51-23.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "编译后，可以在map文件中看到变量和Rte_Task_C0_10ms.c里的代码已经放到对应的DDR地址"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_10-53-52.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_10-53-52.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "通过劳特巴赫调试器观察验证 ："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "可以看到加载到DDR的代码和变量执行正常"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8DDR%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C/image-2025-11-5_11-1-15.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3. 代码和变量放在DDR运行/image-2025-11-5_11-1-15.png"
    }
  ],
